{"type": "article", "id": 16289, "title": "Biophilia 瓷器系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-20T06:30:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160157Qn37NmStcU2AD6OL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套瓷器包括四个部分，黑色的碗“Capsula”代表了子房，白色的有褶皱边的花瓶是主干，灰色的细长“Truncus”是分支，上面放着装饰用的陶器 “Spore”是孢子。四个部分暗示了植物的生根发展过程，可以单独作为花瓶，或是叠加在一起。它们本身的故事性让这个设计充满活力。<a href=\"http://dennyakartan.tictail.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143615jEYQZ7sLPSI3mwge.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143616AcSDOBQZiIfmTdNM.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143616qLZrQHjK7nzVhWNG.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261436171MIXim0JbvecqBZQ.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}